  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Methods: 103 participants, after being randomized to medical versus sham acupuncture received
      bi-weekly treatments for 5 weeks, after a baseline assessment week. They were then followed
      for an additional 7 weeks. Participants completed daily hot flash questionnaires, which
      formed the basis for analysis.
    </textblock>
